      Subclasses of ContainerExecutor in org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.nodemanager 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  DefaultContainerExecutor
      The DefaultContainerExecuter class offers generic container execution services.
      class  DockerContainerExecutor
      Deprecated. 
      The DockerContainerExecutor class has several limitations, not the least of which is that if used, all containers are launched in Docker containers. The LinuxContainerExecutor supports selectively launching containers in Docker containers and should be used instead.
      class  LinuxContainerExecutor
      This class provides Container execution using a native container-executor binary.
      class  WindowsSecureContainerExecutor
      Windows secure container executor (WSCE).
